title: Tetryonics QM 09 - Mesons
description:
QM 09 - Mesons

The sub-atomic geometry of Quark-antiQuark pairings in Tetryonics [the Charged geometry of mass-ENERGY-Matter].

Providing a window on the geometry and decay paths of all Mesons as prescribed by their Tetryonic geometries.

The geometries and interaction angles of Charged 24nPi geometries is revealed for the first time in recorded history.

An updated version of the ninth chapter in the premier release of Tetryonics - The Charged geometry of mass-ENERGY-Matter it serves as an introduction to the geometric maths behind the Science of the new millennia.
